THE BOOK OF RACON:

The 40 Laws (Book of Racon) are included in this repository as
philosophical foundation. They are not code, but they inform all
code. They are not requirements, but they are principles. They
are not suggestionsâ€”they are the foundation.

Use them. Adapt them. But respect them.

"The old laws still hold."
